{"tid":1330946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我是6月9日上街的103萬分之一， 我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-07-18T18:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:48:47.000Z","uid":271176,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"026a861d7952eec325df17497531b07d4d490520","tid":1330946,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"6月9日經歷高溫和驟雨在街上走了幾個小時， 聽到林鄭政府說仍然會堅持進行二讀，我的心情是既憤怒又絕望<br />\n<br />\n6月12日有人號召要前往立法會阻止二讀， 我不夠膽，我怕受傷，我怕被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n誰不怕呢？ 面對的是裝備精良的警隊， 過往多次使用不合理武力， 把示威者打得頭破血流 的警隊。<br />\n<br />\n然後我發現原來香港真的有一大批人 ，無所畏懼， 全賴他們的勇敢 ，條例終於被暫緩。<br />\n<br />\n 他們不是暴徒， 他們是勇者。<br />\n<br />\n是林鄭教他們和平是沒有用的<br />\n是警隊教他們最低武力是怎樣的<br />\n<br />\n一切的始作俑者是林鄭，但是他只是出來聲稱真誠道歉而不用付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n付出代價的是誰呢？<br />\n612當日為我們而衝的勇者正被搜捕<br />\n教育我們下一代何謂公義的老師正被清算<br />\n夠治傷患的醫護被施以下馬威<br />\n採訪衝突的記者被辱罵<br />\n政府正磨刀霍霍迎向區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n我們不能輸這場仗了。 這個運動的結果將會斷定香港未來是光明還是黑暗，是自由還是專制，是世界的頂級城市或僅是大灣區的一部分<br />\n<br />\n無論這個運動要持續多久，我還是全力支持;無論途中發生什麼事情，我還是全力支持。 無論 再多的分化抹黑冷待，我還是全力支持<br />\n<br />\n謹此宣言 ，五大訴求，不達成，不退場。<br />\n<br />\n721港島見"},{"pid":"ac37b259c21881fa5ae8e72cbfd87e56e9abdc34","tid":1330946,"uid":271176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:32:33.000Z","msg":"頭條新聞這段片真係睇到喊，我們不能失去更多了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gjCxLtRxDTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgjCxLtRxDTI&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=158f7ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gjCxLtRxDTI</a>"},{"pid":"72f405413d81db93f8a6a5b865333d918f1e11b0","tid":1330946,"uid":236471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:39:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>五大訴求 義士一個不能少</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好忘記6，7月黑警點對我地班義士</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有好多兄弟等我地救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>721 三點維園</strong></span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">頭盔 電筒必備</span></span></div></div>"},{"pid":"ede679211a50b5fd06b4203f6f8901ad952aa907","tid":1330946,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:41:28.000Z","msg":"幫推。721維園見<br />\n<br />\n【721整合】721整合Post！全部推哂上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"10ac8ed3bfe33941dd8710f8b2b3198083839d4a","tid":1330946,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"希望69 616出來的人再出來一次，我們真的不能再輸"},{"pid":"b464253cf998e14893bab77a85a72a89167a2f1f","tid":1330946,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"721 五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZq16eo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZq16eo.png&h=97f80309&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"548f86c0950b251cdf16d5d45594febcb9f87996","tid":1330946,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"721港島見"},{"pid":"af7e625ab762f36922733173c24ff80abc669c3b","tid":1330946,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:31:30.000Z","msg":"最後一推，明天港島見"},{"pid":"fefd456d0e84b55ea87acec29b4fa1d001c97e05","tid":1330946,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"612 衝擊完被暴力清場 政府係無暫緩<br />\n613 收到習總Order先焗住跪底<br />\n最有用係朝早包圍阻左開會<br />\n唔好又神化衝擊作用"}]}